folder=Zenitha

Summary[dnd-info]=Nestled amidst the tranquil embrace of the northern seas lies the enigmatic island of Zethina. Cloaked in a shroud of untamed wilderness, this mystical realm unveils a tapestry of ancient forests, soaring mountains, and cascading waterfalls that sing haunting melodies. Devoid of human settlements and untouched by the trappings of civilization, Zethina remains an untamed sanctuary where nature reigns supreme. Legends whisper of its deep-rooted connection to the mystical realms, drawing forth beings of unimaginable power and ethereal beauty. The lush verdure conceals secrets within its dense foliage, and the towering peaks harbor untold wonders waiting to be discovered. With each step upon its hallowed grounds, one treads upon the threshold of a realm both magnificent and mysterious, where the echoes of forgotten lore intertwine with the primal pulse of the land.

